One person died and 17 others were injured injured in a collision between a car and a minibus taxi on the R33 in the Mpolweni area near Pietermaritzburg on Saturday afternoon. ER24 paramedics as well as various other services attended to the accident, ER24 spokeswoman Chitra Bodasing-Harduth said. Sadly there was nothing that could be done for one patient. The person was declared dead. All other patients were assessed and found to have sustained injuries ranging from minor to serious. They were treated and transported to local hospitals for further medical care. The cause of the accident was unknown, she said